       "</style><pre class='xr-text-repr-fallback'>&lt;xarray.Dataset&gt; Size: 8GB\n",
       "Dimensions:  (time: 1488, lat: 360, lon: 720)\n",
       "Coordinates:\n",
       "  * time     (time) datetime64[ns] 12kB 1901-01-16 1901-02-15 ... 1900-01-01\n",
       "  * lat      (lat) float32 1kB -89.75 -89.25 -88.75 -88.25 ... 88.75 89.25 89.75\n",
       "  * lon      (lon) float32 3kB -179.8 -179.2 -178.8 -178.2 ... 178.8 179.2 179.8\n",
       "Data variables:\n",
       "    tmp      (time, lat, lon) float32 2GB ...\n",
